# LLM-assisted: Claude Code (claude-sonnet-4-6), 2026-06-25
# Variant: global syntax cache with epoch-counter invalidation
# Materially different from baseline: cache location is a single global array
# (not per-pattern), invalidation uses a global epoch counter that is bumped
# whenever the syntax table changes (not recompile-triggered), and the cache
# can serve any number of patterns without per-pattern storage.
